All threes in one hectare from Barro Colorado Island..

Source: R/data.R

One hectare of data for hectare: px >= 700 and px < 800; and py >=100 and py < 200. The data includes only those records from census 2005 and census 2010.

vft_1ha_bci

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 10543 rows and 32 columns.

Details

This is a slightly cleaned version from a ViewFullTable table. For a raw .csv version see http://bit.ly/fgeo-opendata-vft-1ha-bci.
